You can add to the XHTML-based and PDF published outputs syntax highlight inside these
      codeblock sections, by setting the outputclass attribute on the
        codeblock element to a specific value depending on the content type: 

language-xml;

language-java; 

language-css;

language-javascript;

language-sql;

language-c;

language-cpp;

language-csharp;

language-ini;

language-php;

language-python;

language-ruby;

language-perl;

language-bourne.
